<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Guide Orientation Post-Bac 2026 — Neybras Family</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --aubergine: #6B3A5C;
    --aubergine-dark: #4A2540;
    --aubergine-light: #8B5A7C;
    --terracotta: #DCAD8A;
    --terracotta-light: #ECC9A8;
    --ivory: #F0EDE6;
    --ivory-dark: #E4E0D8;
    --white: #FDFBF7;
    --text-dark: #2C1A26;
    --text-mid: #6B3A5C;
    --text-light: #9A7A8A;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--text-dark);
    overflow-x: hidden;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: var(--aubergine-dark);
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 60px 24px 80px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -120px; right: -120px;
    width: 500px; height: 500px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(107,58,92,0.6) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -80px; left: -80px;
    width: 380px; height: 380px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(220,173,138,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* grain overlay */
  .hero-grain {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; text-align: center; max-width: 640px; }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 1px solid rgba(220,173,138,0.5);
    color: var(--terracotta);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 6px 18px;
    border-radius: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--terracotta-light);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease both;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(38px, 7vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both;
  }

  .hero-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--terracotta);
  }

  .hero-year {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(18px, 4vw, 28px);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(240,237,230,0.6);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease both;
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(240,237,230,0.8);
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto 44px;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease both;
  }

  /* ── FORM ── */
  .form-wrap {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(220,173,138,0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px 28px;
    max-width: 440px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    animation: fadeUp 1.1s ease both;
  }

  .form-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--white);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .form-sub {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(240,237,230,0.55);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .form-group { margin-bottom: 14px; }

  .form-group input {
    width: 100%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(220,173,138,0.25);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--white);
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
  }

  .form-group input::placeholder { color: rgba(240,237,230,0.35); }

  .form-group input:focus {
    border-color: var(--terracotta);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  }

  .btn-primary {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--terracotta);
    color: var(--aubergine-dark);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--terracotta-light); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-primary:active { transform: translateY(0); }

  .form-privacy {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(240,237,230,0.35);
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* success state */
  .form-success {
    display: none;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
  }

  .form-success .checkmark {
    width: 56px; height: 56px;
    background: rgba(220,173,138,0.15);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    font-size: 24px;
  }

  .form-success h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .form-success p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(240,237,230,0.65);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-scroll {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 28px; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    color: rgba(240,237,230,0.3);
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
    animation: fadeUp 1.4s ease both;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px; height: 32px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(220,173,138,0.5), transparent);
    animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  /* ── BENEFITS ── */
  .benefits {
    background: var(--ivory);
    padding: 80px 24px;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--terracotta);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 40px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--aubergine-dark);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .section-sub {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto 60px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .benefit-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px 28px;
    border: 1px solid var(--ivory-dark);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .benefit-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--aubergine), var(--terracotta));
  }

  .benefit-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(107,58,92,0.1); }

  .benefit-icon {
    width: 44px; height: 44px;
    background: rgba(107,58,92,0.08);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .benefit-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--aubergine-dark);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .benefit-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  /* ── CONTENTS ── */
  .contents {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 80px 24px;
  }

  .contents-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .chapters {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    margin-top: 48px;
    border: 1px solid var(--ivory-dark);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .chapter {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 22px 28px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ivory-dark);
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }

  .chapter:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .chapter:hover { background: var(--ivory); }

  .chapter-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--terracotta);
    opacity: 0.6;
    min-width: 36px;
    line-height: 1;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }

  .chapter-text h4 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--aubergine-dark);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .chapter-text p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ── STATS ── */
  .stats-band {
    background: var(--aubergine);
    padding: 60px 24px;
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr));
    gap: 40px;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--terracotta);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: rgba(240,237,230,0.65);
    line-height: 1.4;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ── ABOUT ── */
  .about {
    background: var(--ivory);
    padding: 80px 24px;
  }

  .about-inner {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) { .about-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .about-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--aubergine-dark);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .about-logo {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .logo-mark {
    width: 120px; height: 120px;
    background: var(--aubergine-dark);
    border-radius: 24px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .logo-mark span:first-child {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--terracotta);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .logo-mark span:last-child {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .about-tagline {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── BOTTOM CTA ── */
  .bottom-cta {
    background: var(--aubergine-dark);
    padding: 80px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .bottom-cta::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -60px; right: -60px;
    width: 300px; height: 300px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(220,173,138,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .bottom-cta h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 38px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .bottom-cta p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(240,237,230,0.65);
    max-width: 420px;
    margin: 0 auto 36px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    position: relative;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--terracotta);
    color: var(--terracotta);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    position: relative;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--terracotta);
    color: var(--aubergine-dark);
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: #1E0F1A;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  footer p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(240,237,230,0.3);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  footer a { color: var(--terracotta); text-decoration: none; }

  /* ── DIVIDER ── */
  .divider {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
    max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 60px;
  }
  .divider-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--ivory-dark); }
  .divider-dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--terracotta); opacity: 0.5; }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes scrollPulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; }
    50%       { opacity: 0.8; }
  }

  /* scroll reveal */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .form-wrap { padding: 24px 18px; }
    .benefit-card { padding: 24px 20px; }
    .chapter { padding: 18px 20px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-grain"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="badge">Guide exclusif — Téléchargement gratuit</div>
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Neybras Family · Édition 2026</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Guide complet<br><em>orientation</em><br>post-bac</h1>
    <p class="hero-year">au Maroc — 2026</p>
    <p class="hero-desc">Filières, coûts réels, CPGE, études à l'étranger, plan d'action étape par étape. Tout ce que les familles marocaines CSP+ doivent savoir pour prendre les meilleures décisions.</p>

    <div class="form-wrap">
      <div class="form-title">Recevez le guide gratuitement</div>
      <p class="form-sub">Votre guide PDF arrive dans votre boite mail en moins de 2 minutes</p>

      <div id="mainForm">
        <div class="form-group">
          <input type="text" id="firstName" placeholder="Votre prénom" autocomplete="given-name">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <input type="email" id="emailInput" placeholder="Votre adresse email" autocomplete="email">
        </div>
        <button class="btn-primary" onclick="handleSubmit()">
          Télécharger le guide →
        </button>
        <p class="form-privacy">🔒 Aucun spam. Vos données restent confidentielles. Désabonnement en 1 clic.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="form-success" id="successMsg">
        <div class="checkmark">✓</div>
        <h3>Guide envoyé !</h3>
        <p>Vérifiez votre boite mail dans les 2 prochaines minutes. Bienvenue dans la communauté Neybras Family.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-scroll">
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
    <span>Découvrir</span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── STATS BAND ── -->
<div class="stats-band">
  <div class="stats-grid reveal">
    <div>
      <div class="stat-num">6</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Filières<br>analysées</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="stat-num">5</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Chapitres<br>pratiques</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="stat-num">4</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Destinations<br>comparées</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="stat-num">100%</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Gratuit<br>& immédiat</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── BENEFITS ── -->
<section class="benefits">
  <p class="section-label reveal">Ce que vous allez découvrir</p>
  <h2 class="section-title reveal">Tout ce que les parents<br>doivent savoir — en un seul guide</h2>
  <p class="section-sub reveal">Conçu par la rédaction de Neybras Family avec des experts de l'orientation marocaine.</p>

  <div class="divider reveal">
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
    <div class="divider-dot"></div>
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="benefits-grid">
    <div class="benefit-card reveal">
      <div class="benefit-icon">🎓</div>
      <h3>Vue d'ensemble des filières</h3>
      <p>CPGE, université publique, grande école privée, BTS, médecine… Chaque voie expliquée clairement avec durée, coût et débouchés.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card reveal">
      <div class="benefit-icon">💰</div>
      <h3>Budget réel sur 3 à 5 ans</h3>
      <p>Scolarité, logement, transport, manuels — les vrais chiffres que les établissements ne vous donnent pas spontanément.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card reveal">
      <div class="benefit-icon">🌍</div>
      <h3>Maroc vs étranger</h3>
      <p>France, Canada, Espagne : comparatif honnête des coûts, des visas, des débouchés et des conditions de vie étudiante.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card reveal">
      <div class="benefit-icon">📋</div>
      <h3>Plan d'action en 6 étapes</h3>
      <p>De janvier à la rentrée — ce qu'il faut faire, quand le faire, et comment maximiser les chances de votre enfant.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card reveal">
      <div class="benefit-icon">🏫</div>
      <h3>Meilleures CPGE du Maroc</h3>
      <p>Classement indépendant, critères de sélection, conseils pour la lettre de motivation et l'entretien d'admission.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card reveal">
      <div class="benefit-icon">⚠️</div>
      <h3>Erreurs à éviter absolument</h3>
      <p>Les 5 erreurs les plus fréquentes des familles marocaines lors de l'orientation — et comment les éviter.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── CONTENTS ── -->
<section class="contents">
  <div class="contents-inner">
    <p class="section-label reveal">Au sommaire</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">5 chapitres complets<br>pour décider sereinement</h2>

    <div class="chapters reveal">
      <div class="chapter">
        <div class="chapter-num">01</div>
        <div class="chapter-text">
          <h4>Vue d'ensemble des filières post-bac</h4>
          <p>Tableau comparatif complet : CPGE, licences, grandes écoles, médecine, BTS</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="chapter">
        <div class="chapter-num">02</div>
        <div class="chapter-text">
          <h4>Les Classes Préparatoires (CPGE)</h4>
          <p>Meilleures CPGE du Maroc, critères de sélection, conseils de candidature</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="chapter">
        <div class="chapter-num">03</div>
        <div class="chapter-text">
          <h4>Les coûts réels des études au Maroc</h4>
          <p>Budget annuel complet par type d'établissement — les chiffres vrais</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="chapter">
        <div class="chapter-num">04</div>
        <div class="chapter-text">
          <h4>Maroc ou étranger : comment choisir ?</h4>
          <p>Comparatif France · Canada · Espagne · Belgique avec les 3 questions décisives</p>
